<body>

<h1>Brief Description</h1>

<p><b>Destroy building</b></p>
<p>Allows the player to destroy the building within his base to free up a cell.</p>

<p><b>Check information about building</b></p>
<p>Allow the Player to check information about a building before creating it or about a building already built on his base.</p>

<p><b>Check information about an unit</b></p>
<p>Allow the Player to check information about a unit before creating it or about a unit already created on his army.</p>

<p><b>Check information about his own base</b></p>
<p>Allow the Player to check global information about his base.</p>

<p><b>Check information about another base</b></p>
<p>Allow the Player to check information about an enemy base on the map.</p>

</body>
</html>
